<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Demande de participation - ${nomEvenement}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 35px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .logo-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 180px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #2980b9;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .event-title {
            color: #2980b9;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .event-subtitle {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .request-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .personal-info {
            background-color: #f0f7fb;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #2980b9;
        }

        .personal-info h3 {
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .personal-info p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .reminder-message {
            background-color: #fff8e6;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #a46900;
        }

        .contact-info {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-top: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="logo-section">
        <img src="https://veevent.vercel.app/veevent.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
    </div>

    <div class="header">
        <h1 class="event-title">Demande de participation</h1>
        <h2 class="event-subtitle">${nomEvenement}</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="request-text">
        <p>Bonjour,</p>
        <p>Une nouvelle personne souhaite rejoindre l'évènement <strong>${nomEvenement}</strong>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="personal-info">
        <h3>Informations du participant</h3>
        <p><strong>Nom :</strong> ${nom}</p>
        <p><strong>Prénom :</strong> ${prenom}</p>
        <p><strong>Email :</strong> ${emailExpediteur}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reminder-message">
        Merci de valider ou refuser cette demande de participation.
    </div>

    <div class="contact-info">
        Candidature envoyée le ${dateEnvoi}
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
